Title: Restore event helper time out to 3s
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Component: core
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0p22
Date: 1613552587

Werk 10619 erroneously changed the event helper time out 
from 3 s (seconds) to 3 ms (milliseconds).  This patch
restores the original time out of 3 s.
